<p>This is cool. I think the ammendum is worded a bit confusingly (the last sentence cuts off at &quot;Recording equipment&quot;) but other than that, sweet. And I'd love to see the folks down below form a miniature foundation of their own, said mini-foundation then realizes what's going on and mass confusion ensues.</p>
